If the app is being released to the general public, stability should be a top priority, Another major issue is its handling of mathematical formulas. Instead of properly rendering equations, it presents them as raw LaTeX code, making it difficult to read and understand. Many AI models today process and display.

Suggestions for Improvement: Regional Language Awareness: Implement automatic region detection.
